  "functionality": "Registers all ID stage outputs (control signals, register addresses/data, immediate, PC, and valid) and makes them available to the EX stage. On reset, clears all registers. On flush, the valid bit is cleared to invalidate the instruction (effectively a bubble). No stall input; stalling is managed in earlier pipeline stages.",
